PIZZA  CORNER WEB APPLICATION

Technologies used : 
	Front-End
	1. HTML
	2. CSS
	3. JavaScript

	Back-End
	1.MySQL
	2.Apache Tomcat
	3.Java

This project is an online portal to order food from pizza corner(Hypothetical). In this project we have created a login through which users can access the cart and buy food and stuff. The payment invoice is sent to the customer as a mail using SMTP mail server. 


